com.phunware.core

Class PwLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.phunware.core.PwLog

  • public final class PwLog
extends java.lang.Object
    Show logs for the MaaS SDKs. Logs are turned off by default. To turn logs on, call setShowLog(boolean) with a trueparameter.

      • setShowLog

        public static void setShowLog(boolean showLog)
        Pass in true to show all PwLogs. Pass in false to hide debug, info and verbose logs that are created by MaaS SDKs.
        Parameters:
        showLog - True to show logs; false to hide logs.
